---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Senior DevOps and Site Reliability Engineer with 4+ years owning production Kubernetes and AWS
    infrastructure. Reduced observability spend by 35%, infrastructure costs by 40%, and incident
    response time by 75% through improved monitoring, alert design, and operational practices.
    Built Terraform-based infrastructure and GitOps workflows, focused on reliability, cost control,
    and capacity planning.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-lg">
      For complete role details and accomplishments, <a href="/JaredKominsky_Base.pdf" class="link link-primary font-semibold" target="_blank">download my full resume (PDF)</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience Themes</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Infrastructure Ownership</div>
    <p class="text-lg mb-2">
      Owned production Kubernetes and AWS infrastructure at Groups360 (2 years) and Built Technologies (7 months). Migrated EKS provisioning to Terraform IaC, drove Argo CD GitOps adoption, and designed multi-AZ resilience with topology spread constraints and anti-affinity rules.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Cost Optimization</div>
    <p class="text-lg mb-2">
      Reduced infrastructure costs by 40% through six months of usage analysis and resource right-sizing. Cut observability spend by 35% via host optimization, log ingestion controls, and APM retention tuning.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Observability & Incident Response</div>
    <p class="text-lg mb-2">
      Reduced incident response time by 75% across 40+ microservices at Built Technologies. Built 30+ actionable monitors at Groups360. Defined SLIs/SLOs aligned with business priorities. Led incident response and post-incident reviews.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Automation & Standards</div>
    <p class="text-lg mb-2">
      Automated management of 200+ GitHub repositories with Terraform at Groups360. Built autoscaling CI infrastructure using GitHub Actions Runner Controller. Reduced CI/CD cycle time by 75% through parallel execution and dependency optimization at Built Technologies.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Personal Platform Project</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-8 p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">UnifyOps — Internal Developer Platform</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-lg space-y-1">
      <li>Built and operate an internal developer platform using Kubernetes, GitOps, and strict runtime isolation</li>
      <li>Designed a three-tier stack model with enforced network boundaries and zero-downtime deploys</li>
      <li>Created a shared core package enforcing logging, auth, and error contracts across services</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-2"><a href="/projects/unifyops" class="link link-primary font-semibold">View deep dive →</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Work History</div>
  </div>

  <TimeLineElement
    title="Site Reliability Engineer"
    subtitle="Groups360, Nashville, TN (Jan 2024 - Jan 2026)"
  >
    <p class="text-lg mb-2">Owned production Kubernetes/AWS infrastructure.</p>
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 mb-1">Key outcomes:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-base space-y-1">
      <li>40% infrastructure cost reduction through usage analysis and right-sizing</li>
      <li>35% observability savings via host optimization and log controls</li>
      <li>Migrated EKS to Terraform IaC and drove Argo CD GitOps adoption</li>
    </ul>
  </TimeLineElement>

  <TimeLineElement
    title="Site Reliability Engineer II"
    subtitle="Built Technologies, Nashville, TN (Jan 2023 - Jul 2023)"
  >
    <p class="text-lg mb-2">Owned observability for 40+ microservices.</p>
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 mb-1">Key outcomes:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-base space-y-1">
      <li>75% faster incident response across 40+ microservices</li>
      <li>Implemented SLIs/SLOs aligned with business priorities</li>
      <li>Integrated PagerDuty into on-call workflows</li>
    </ul>
  </TimeLineElement>

  <TimeLineElement
    title="QA Automation Engineer"
    subtitle="Built Technologies, Nashville, TN (Jan 2022 - Jan 2023)"
  >
    <p class="text-lg mb-2">Owned test automation and CI optimization.</p>
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 mb-1">Key outcomes:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-base space-y-1">
      <li>75% faster CI/CD cycles through parallel execution</li>
      <li>Built Onward Award recipient for sustained impact</li>
    </ul>
  </TimeLineElement>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Awards</div>
  </div>

  <TimeLineElement title="Built Onward Award" subtitle="Built Technologies, Dec 2022">
    <p class="text-lg">Awarded to less than 10% of team members for sustained impact and ownership.</p>
  </TimeLineElement>

  <TimeLineElement
    title="Stephen Campbell Math & Computer Science Award"
    subtitle="Belmont University, 2021"
  >
    <p class="text-lg">Annual award for outstanding achievement in mathematics and computer science.</p>
  </TimeLineElement>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <TimeLineElement
    title="Bachelor of Science in Computer Science, Minor in Entrepreneurship"
    subtitle="Belmont University, Nashville, TN (Graduated Dec 2021)"
  >
    <p class="text-lg">GPA: 3.76 | Dean's List Fall 2019 - Fall 2020</p>
  </TimeLineElement>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Core Skills</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <div class="mb-4">
      <span class="font-semibold">Kubernetes & Container Orchestration:</span>
      EKS, HPA, Pod Disruption Budgets, multi-AZ scheduling, affinity rules
    </div>
    <div class="mb-4">
      <span class="font-semibold">Infrastructure as Code & GitOps:</span>
      Terraform, Helm, Argo CD, GitHub Actions
    </div>
    <div class="mb-4">
      <span class="font-semibold">Cloud Platforms:</span>
      AWS (EKS, RDS, S3, CloudFront, Secrets Manager, IAM)
    </div>
    <div class="mb-4">
      <span class="font-semibold">Observability:</span>
      Datadog (APM, logging, metrics, distributed tracing), SLIs/SLOs
    </div>
    <div class="mb-4">
      <span class="font-semibold">Reliability Engineering:</span>
      Incident response, load testing (k6), capacity planning, cost optimization
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
